content.top_review:
Let’s be clear, this is an “inexpensive” watch.That being said it is a good quality watch for this price point.Easy to operate, light works great, it’s not bright and that’s fine with me as it works fine in the dark.
  
Read more
content.description: Main features: Men's Digital Sport Watch Equipped with alarm, calendar, day, date and stopwatch function. 12/24 hours. See the time clearly in the dark with backlight, easy to read. High quality silicone band, soft and comfortable to wear. 5ATM waterproof, convenient for everyday use. Metal buckle, adjustable straps. Material: Movement: Digital sports watch, waterproof. Wristband: High quality silicone resin band provides a comfortable wearing experience. Mirror surface: highly transparent resin glass, scratch resistant. Case: imported PC case. Button: stainless steel Bottom cover: high quality stainless steel, waterproof. Parameters: Dial diameter: 50 mm. Dial thickness: 17 mm. Band Length: 270mm Band width: 20 mm. Box contents: 1 x sports watch. 1 x User Manual 1 x gift. 1 x watch box. About waterproof watches: Waterproof resistance is tested under static conditions. Wearing a watch that is 50 meters waterproof, the watch will be exposed to much greater pressure than a 50 metre static test. Therefore, the number of metres on the watch does not indicate the depth to which the watch can be taken. These watches can withstand small splashes of water, but should not be worn when washing hands or immersing hands in water. Please do not pull out the buttons underwater, frequent contact with water would reduce the life of the watch. Clean the watch with a soft cloth and wipe it gently.
